<control ref='GOOGLE-LOG02' name='Create mechanisms to periodically export the Audit Logs' platform='' cost='1' risk='0' state='Recommended' owner='' library='' source='MANUAL'>
          <desc>Enable the exporting of information from the Audit Logs to save them in a storage account.&amp;nbsp;
                        &lt;div&gt;
                        &lt;br /&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div&gt;
                        &lt;b&gt;Remediation:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div&gt;
                        &lt;ol&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Go to the Logs Viewer and pick a project.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Select Exports in the left-side navigation panel.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;We want to export all audit logs, therefore select the All logs checkbox.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Select the corresponding Storage bucket in the section &amp;quot;Save to Cloud Storage
                        bucket&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li&gt;Click &amp;quot;Save&amp;quot; button.&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;/ol&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                    </desc>
